aineruniface_104rmh1665702535076.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rmh1665702535076.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rmh1665702535076.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rmh1665702535076\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Returns <code class=\"ph codeph\">true</code> if the view is valid.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"rmh1665702535076__topic_d127430e1_d127431e1_d127432e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rmh1665702535076__p_d127433e1_d127434e1_d127435e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">unifaceViewObject</var>.<span class=\"keyword apiname\">isValid()</span>\n</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rmh1665702535076__section_w1385ab1b5b3_w1386ab1b5_w1387ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d970319e67\">Return Value</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rmh1665702535076__p_d127439e1_d127440e1_d127441e1\">Returns <code class=\"ph codeph\">true</code> if the View object is\n            valid; otherwise <code class=\"ph codeph\">false</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rmh1665702535076__section_w1388ab1b5b5_w1389ab1b5_w1390ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d970319e82\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rmh1665702535076__p_d127445e1_d127446e1_d127447e1\">Use the <span class=\"keyword apiname\">isValid()</span> function check\n            whether the view is valid before using the <span class=\"keyword apiname\">show()</span> function.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"rmh1665702535076__note_a477938c745598891bbe27e5cc848485\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> This function does not work\n            with the default view that is automatically created by the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">weblayout</span>\n            ProcScript command.</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bott